@baseUrl = http://localhost:3333
@scheduleId = 1
@accessToken = COLE_SEU_TOKEN_AQUI

### [SUCESSO] Atualizar horário existente
# Esperado: 200 com horário atualizado
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/schedules/{{scheduleId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "dayOfWeek": "tuesday",
  "startTime": "08:00",
  "endTime": "12:00"
}

###

### [SUCESSO] Atualizar mantendo mesmo horário (sem conflito consigo mesmo)
# Esperado: 200 — o próprio registro é ignorado na checagem de conflito
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/schedules/{{scheduleId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "dayOfWeek": "monday",
  "startTime": "09:00",
  "endTime": "12:00"
}

###

### [FALHA] Horário inexistente
# Esperado: 404 NotFoundError
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/schedules/999999
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "dayOfWeek": "tuesday",
  "startTime": "08:00",
  "endTime": "12:00"
}

###

### [FALHA] Atualização gera conflito com outro horário existente
# Esperado: 409 ConflictError
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/schedules/{{scheduleId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "dayOfWeek": "monday",
  "startTime": "10:00",
  "endTime": "16:00"
}

###

### [FALHA] ID inválido no path
# Esperado: 422 Validation Error
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/schedules/abc
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "dayOfWeek": "monday",
  "startTime": "09:00",
  "endTime": "17:00"
}

###

### [FALHA] dayOfWeek ausente no body
# Esperado: 422 Validation Error com campo dayOfWeek nos issues
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/schedules/{{scheduleId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "startTime": "09:00",
  "endTime": "17:00"
}

###

### [FALHA] startTime >= endTime
# Esperado: 422 Validation Error com campo startTime nos issues
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/schedules/{{scheduleId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "dayOfWeek": "monday",
  "startTime": "17:00",
  "endTime": "09:00"
}

###

### [FALHA] Sem token de autenticação
# Esperado: 401 UnauthorizedError
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/schedules/{{scheduleId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "dayOfWeek": "tuesday",
  "startTime": "08:00",
  "endTime": "12:00"
}

###

### [FALHA] Token de outro prestador (sem permissão para atualizar este horário)
# Pré-requisito: @accessToken pertence ao prestador id=2; horário id=1 pertence ao id=1
# Esperado: 403 ForbiddenError
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/schedules/{{scheduleId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "dayOfWeek": "tuesday",
  "startTime": "08:00",
  "endTime": "12:00"
}
